Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人闯了点祸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老手也别放松警惕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 知道了
